                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18240916-74-off397 t18240916-74-cd398"></join>, a purse, value 6 d.; two sovereigns, and three shillings, the property of 
                     
                        <persName id="t18240916-74-victim665" type="victimName">
